<div>Upload a photo of your decorated tree, and get your friends to vote! A winner will be chosen out of the top 4 ranked trees, We’ll pick based on number of votes but also on the trees originality and creativity. Competition closes at midnight Tuesday 22nd of December and we’ll announce the winner after that! The prize is a Makita EA3200S Chainsaw! (Thanks to Onehunga Powertool Centre and Makita Tools for this fantastic prize valued at $508).</div>




