       <h1 class="entry-title">
        Home
       </h1>
       <div class="entry-content">
        <h2>
         Open from 25th November – 9AM to 7PM
        </h2>
        <h2>
         Ever wanted to cut your own Christmas tree?
        </h2>
        <div>
         <img alt="" class="alignright size-medium wp-image-159" height="300" sizes="(max-width: 269px) 100vw, 269px" src="http://christmastrees.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-tree-031-269x300.jpg" srcset="https://christmastrees.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-tree-031-269x300.jpg 269w, https://christmastrees.co.nz/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/jc-tree-031.jpg 300w" title="jc tree 03" width="269"/>
         Come on out to one of our three farms at Mt Gabriel and find out what it’s like to choose and take home one of the freshest, best shaped Christmas trees you’ve ever had. You can even cut your own tree if you desire or our friendly staff will assist you.
        </div>
        <div>
         <strong>
          Real Christmas trees priced from only $25.
         </strong>
        </div>
        <div>
        </div>
        <div>
         <div class="fb_reset" id="fb-root">
          <div style="position: absolute; top: -10000px; width: 0px; height: 0px;">
           <div>
